end_on.description: The localized end date of the time period in `YYYY-MM-DD` format.

start_on.description: The localized start date of the time period in `YYYY-MM-DD` format.

period.description: The cadence and index of the time period. The value is one of: `FY`, `H1`, `H2`, `Q1`, `Q2`, `Q3`, or `Q4`.

display_name.description: A string representing the cadence code and the fiscal year.
